  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nTo make it easier to use and create tags (and server side components), it is important to be able to allow passing random args to any underlying element of the tag (determined by the implementation).\r\n\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\ngravatar.html\r\n```html\r\n<img src=\"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/{hash}{#if size}?s={size}{/if}\" {params.without(\"hash\", \"size\").asHtmlAttributes()}/>\r\n```\r\n\r\nUsage:\r\n```html\r\n{#gravatar hash=\"ia3andy\" alt=\"ia3andy\" title=\"https://github.com/ia3andy\" class=rounded}\r\n```\r\n\r\nOutput:\r\n```html\r\n<img src=\"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/ia3andy\" alt=\"ia3andy\" title=\"https://github.com/ia3andy\" class=\"rounded\" />\r\n```",
